Virus Encyclopedia

Adware.Generic
What is Adware and Spyware?

The strange manners of the Internet Explorer on your PC (automatic pop up of the web pages with a suspicious commercial content) or automatic redirection of your home page to the another one (as described - erotics, warez,etc.) may not be caused by the presence of the virus but the other malware also known as ADWARE or SPYWARE. 

These programs are being installed during the time you browse some Internet pages of the commercial content (mainly erotics, warez, music downloads). 

These programs are not viruses and thats why they even can't be detected as viruses (by antivirus program). If you are using the AVG version 7.1, it's possible that the AVG will detect some of these unwanted programs. Even so there are many programs capable to remove this stuff. For example Ad-aware or Spybot - both as freeware version available too. We recommend to search the Internet for more.
